description:
Case #0181606


Statement of Manuela Dominguez regarding the fall of the Church of the Divine Host


Audio recording by Jonathan Sims, the Archivist.


Thanks to this week's Patrons: Cait F, Morrow Grove, Elizabeth Cornwell, Kerry Lloyd, Casey Peavler, Flighty Broad, Rebecca Coffey, Tatum B, Addy Bats, Gladys Gonzalez, Zedd Newton-Whitaker, Anna Z, Megan Griffin, Emptyface Buttercup, Kathryn Cwynar, Kylee Berry, Emily Johnson, John Cullen, Metrophor, Meghan O'Grady


If you'd like to join them be sure to visit www.patreon.com/rustyquill


Edited this week by Elizabeth Moffatt, Brock Winstead & Alexander J Newall.


Written by Jonathan Sims and directed by Alexander J Newall.


Performances:

- "The Archivist" - Jonathan Sims

- "Basira Hussain" - Frank Voss

- "Manuela Dominguez " - Layla Mannings

- "Helen Richardson" - Imogen Harris


Sound effects this week by previously credited artists via freesound.org.
